Blocked
=======

An apology is missing.

Those are being blocked until enough confident and trust is re-established. 
These people severely violated the code of conduct or acceptable coding
quality multiple times (calling names, revert wars, block blocking tickets,
committing questionable code to master directly, no ticket, ...) or have not
enough technical capabilities.  They do have voting rights though, and pull
requests will be handled properly.

